									<div class="gravatar"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/cindyjuyoungok/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Cindy_Juyoung_Ok-headshot-100x100.jpeg" width="100" height="100" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Cindy_Juyoung_Ok-headshot-300x300.jpeg 2x" alt="Cindy Juyoung Ok" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></a></div>
									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/cindyjuyoungok/">Cindy Juyoung Ok</a></h6>
										Cindy Juyoung Ok is the author of <em>Ward Toward</em>, a finalist for the <em>Los Angeles Times</em> Book Prize and the National Book Critics Circle John Leonard Prize, and the translator of <em>The Hell of That Star</em> by Kim Hyesoon.																			</div>
